data.description: Are you ready to go home for the holidays? This beautiful home nestled in the highly sought after neighborhood of Mabry Park is perfect for you! It hosts 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. It also has a flex room that could be an office, play room, or a landing zone. Enjoy conversations with your neighbors on your front porch, or relax on the backyard patio with views of nature and wildlife. The master suite has ample room for a sitting area and the attic has plenty of storage space.  This home won't last long, so schedule your showing today!
